Dialogue: 0,0:00:03.98,0:00:05.24,Kingdom-Thought,Tian,0,0,0,,Lian Po... {Thought}
Dialogue: 0,0:00:04.20,0:00:06.77,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,（蒙恬(もうてん)）廉頗(れんぱ)が負けを認めた？
Dialogue: 0,0:00:05.24,0:00:06.85,Kingdom-Thought,Tian,0,0,0,,admitted his defeat?! {Thought}
Dialogue: 0,0:00:06.90,0:00:09.77,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,（信(しん)）えっ… 勝ったのか？
Dialogue: 0,0:00:08.17,0:00:12.11,Kingdom-Thought,Xin,0,0,0,,We... won?  {Thought}
Dialogue: 0,0:00:10.67,0:00:11.98,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,（信）俺たちが…
Dialogue: 0,0:00:14.86,0:00:19.82,Kingdom - Episode Title,Title,0,0,0,,{\fs80\be0.2\c&H000000&\pos(500,100)}Victory... And...
Dialogue: 0,0:00:20.38,0:00:23.09,Kingdom-Main,Jie,0,0,0,,What are you saying, my lord?!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:20.55,0:00:22.85,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,（介子坊(かいしぼう)）\N何をおっしゃるのですか 殿！
Dialogue: 0,0:00:22.95,0:00:25.69,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,勝負は まだ決しておりませぬぞ！
Dialogue: 0,0:00:23.09,0:00:26.11,Kingdom-Main,Jie,0,0,0,,Victory or defeat has certainly not yet been decided!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:26.11,0:00:28.95,Kingdom-Main,Jie,0,0,0,,If we slay Meng Ao, the state of battle will be even!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:26.32,0:00:28.73,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,蒙驁(もうごう)を討ち取れば 戦況は五分
Dialogue: 0,0:00:28.83,0:00:34.23,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,そこから今度こそ殿が大将となって\N立て直せば 勝機は必ず…
Dialogue: 0,0:00:28.95,0:00:32.16,Kingdom-Main,Jie,0,0,0,,And then, if we regroup with you as the Great General, my lord,
Dialogue: 0,0:00:32.16,0:00:34.41,Kingdom-Main,Jie,0,0,0,,our victory will be certain!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:35.13,0:00:36.40,Kingdom-Main,Guy,0,0,0,,That's right!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:35.33,0:00:39.67,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,（魏(ぎ)兵）そうだ！ ここには\N廉頗将軍と介子坊将軍がおられる！
Dialogue: 0,0:00:36.40,0:00:39.89,Kingdom-Main,Guy,0,0,0,,We have both General Lian Po and General Jie Zifang here!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:39.77,0:00:41.81,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,（魏兵）蒙驁を討つのは たやすい
Dialogue: 0,0:00:39.89,0:00:41.89,Kingdom-Main,Guy,0,0,0,,Slaying Meng Ao will be an easy task!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:41.89,0:00:44.14,Kingdom-Main,Guy,0,0,0,,Let's do it, General!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:41.94,0:00:44.01,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,（魏兵）やりましょう 将軍！\N（蒙恬）ンッ…
Dialogue: 0,0:00:44.14,0:00:46.75,Kingdom-Main,Guy,0,0,0,,That's right! We can still win!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:44.34,0:00:47.61,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,（魏兵）そうです！ まだ勝てます\N（信）クッ… てめえら
Dialogue: 0,0:00:46.75,0:00:47.64,Kingdom-Main,Xin,0,0,0,,You guys...
Dialogue: 0,0:00:57.33,0:00:59.16,Kingdom-Main,Lian,0,0,0,,It's useless.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:57.69,0:00:59.02,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,（廉頗）ムダじゃ
Dialogue: 0,0:00:59.16,0:01:02.16,Kingdom-Main,Lian,0,0,0,,This war is already over.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:59.36,0:01:02.03,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,この戦は もう詰んでおる
Dialogue: 0,0:01:04.57,0:01:07.16,Kingdom-Thought,Tian,0,0,0,,The war... is over?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:04.66,0:01:07.03,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,戦が詰んでる？
Dialogue: 0,0:01:09.69,0:01:12.54,Kingdom-Main,Lian,0,0,0,,If you take a look at the battlefield as a whole...
Dialogue: 0,0:01:09.83,0:01:12.54,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,（廉頗）戦場全体を見渡せば―
Dialogue: 0,0:01:12.54,0:01:22.05,Kingdom - Titles Ep 33,Sign,0,0,0,,{\be1\fs48\pos(835,116)}Left Army{Top}
Dialogue: 0,0:01:12.54,0:01:22.05,Kingdom - Titles Ep 33,Sign,0,0,0,,{\be1\fs48\pos(574,459)}State of\NQin Army {Center}
Dialogue: 0,0:01:12.54,0:01:22.05,Kingdom - Titles Ep 33,Sign,0,0,0,,{\be1\fs48\pos(1003,426)}Head Quarters {Center, same bubble}
Dialogue: 0,0:01:12.54,0:01:22.05,Kingdom - Titles Ep 33,Sign,0,0,0,,{\be1\fs48\pos(266,138)}Central Army {Left}
Dialogue: 0,0:01:12.54,0:01:22.05,Kingdom - Titles Ep 33,Sign,0,0,0,,{\be1\fs48\pos(159,483)}Right Army {Bottom Left}
Dialogue: 0,0:01:12.67,0:01:17.77,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,介子坊の左軍の ほとんどは\Nいまだ 山中に散ったまま
Dialogue: 0,0:01:12.70,0:01:17.88,Kingdom-Main,Lian,0,0,0,,Right now Jie Zifang's left army is still scattered throughout the mountains.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:17.87,0:01:21.95,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,中央軍は輪虎(りんこ)を失い もはや力なく
Dialogue: 0,0:01:17.88,0:01:22.07,Kingdom-Main,Lian,0,0,0,,With the central army having lost Lun Hu, it's now powerless.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:22.07,0:01:26.20,Kingdom-Main,Lian,0,0,0,,And Jiang Yan's right army has fallen back to the mountains.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:22.28,0:01:25.82,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,姜燕(きょうえん)の右軍も 後方の山中にある
Dialogue: 0,0:01:26.20,0:01:31.56,Kingdom-Main,Lian,0,0,0,,If we had enough time, we, the State of Wei Army could regroup.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:26.28,0:01:31.55,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,それなりの時があれば\Nわしは魏国軍をここから立て直せる
Dialogue: 0,0:01:32.25,0:01:35.57,Kingdom-Main,Lian,0,0,0,,But there is a factor that will not allow that.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:32.49,0:01:35.56,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,しかし それを許さぬ存在がある
Dialogue: 0,0:01:36.82,0:01:41.65,Kingdom-Main,Lian,0,0,0,,The man watching over the state of battle in a the mountain fortress far in the rear,
Dialogue: 0,0:01:36.89,0:01:43.30,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,後方の山城の中で\Nじっと戦況を見守っている王翦(おうせん)じゃ
Dialogue: 0,0:01:41.65,0:01:43.31,Kingdom-Main,Lian,0,0,0,,Wang Jian.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:43.82,0:01:49.94,Kingdom-Main,Lian,0,0,0,,With his army's power largely undamaged, he is awaiting a chance to sortie.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:43.90,0:01:47.07,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,（廉頗）ヤツは\N軍の力をほぼ無傷に保ったまま―
Dialogue: 0,0:01:47.37,0:01:49.81,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,出撃の機会をうかがっておる
Dialogue: 0,0:01:49.91,0:01:56.38,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,この状況で 全力で戦える万の軍が\N出現するというのは 決定打となる
Dialogue: 0,0:01:49.94,0:01:56.34,Kingdom-Main,Lian,0,0,0,,With the battle in this state, the appearance of an army of 10,000, fully able to fight, would be a decisive blow.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:56.74,0:01:59.84,Kingdom-Thought,Xin,0,0,0,,Wang Jian... Wang Ben's dad, huh? {Thought}
Dialogue: 0,0:01:56.95,0:01:59.78,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,王翦… 王賁(おうほん)の親父(おやじ)か
Dialogue: 0,0:01:59.84,0:02:02.40,Kingdom-Main,Jie,0,0,0,,But for Wang Jian, we have Jiang Yan...
Dialogue: 0,0:01:59.92,0:02:04.59,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,しかし 王翦に対しては姜燕が…\N（廉頗）足止め程度じゃ
Dialogue: 0,0:02:02.40,0:02:04.85,Kingdom-Main,Lian,0,0,0,,Just enough to stop him.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:04.85,0:02:09.64,Kingdom-Main,Lian,0,0,0,,If Wang Jian acts, he's certain to go after me.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:04.92,0:02:07.02,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,王翦が出てくれば―
Dialogue: 0,0:02:07.32,0:02:12.63,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,わしは 必ず背を追われ\N全軍の立て直しが利かなくなる
Dialogue: 0,0:02:09.64,0:02:12.71,Kingdom-Main,Lian,0,0,0,,And then I won't be able to reorganize our armies.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:12.71,0:02:17.86,Kingdom-Main,Lian,0,0,0,,With the many armies scattered all over, Huan Ji will ruthlessly mow them down
Dialogue: 0,0:02:12.73,0:02:17.80,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,そして バラバラになった各軍を\N桓騎(かんき)が 冷酷に刈り取っていき…
Dialogue: 0,0:02:17.86,0:02:20.75,Kingdom-Main,Lian,0,0,0,,and the State of Wei Army will be annihilated.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:17.93,0:02:21.81,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,魏国軍は全滅じゃ\N（介子坊）グッ…
Dialogue: 0,0:02:21.83,0:02:26.93,Kingdom-Main,Lian,0,0,0,,If we're considering the best interest of the State of Wei, we must avoid that at all costs.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:21.91,0:02:26.71,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,魏国のことを考えるなら\Nそれだけは回避せねばならぬ
Dialogue: 0,0:02:26.81,0:02:27.81,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,しかし！
Dialogue: 0,0:02:26.93,0:02:27.87,Kingdom-Main,Jie,0,0,0,,But...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:34.12,0:02:35.45,Kingdom-Main,Bi,0,0,0,,Go!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:34.38,0:02:37.82,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,（壁(へき)）\N行けー！ 蒙驁将軍を助けるのだ！
Dialogue: 0,0:02:35.45,0:02:37.90,Kingdom-Main,Bi,0,0,0,,Save General Meng Ao!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:37.90,0:02:40.14,Kingdom-Main,Guy,0,0,0,,A fresh supply of State of Qin soldiers are coming!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:37.95,0:02:42.03,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,下から秦国(しんこく)の新手が来ます！\Nその数 およそ2,000！
Dialogue: 0,0:02:40.14,0:02:42.21,Kingdom-Main,Guy,0,0,0,,They look to be... about 2,000!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:42.13,0:02:43.83,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,（隊長）な… なに！
Dialogue: 0,0:02:42.21,0:02:43.89,Kingdom-Main,Guys,0,0,0,,What?!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:43.89,0:02:45.25,Kingdom-Main,Guys,0,0,0,,General!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:43.96,0:02:45.96,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,将軍！\N（介子坊）クッ…
Dialogue: 0,0:02:45.99,0:02:47.89,Kingdom-Main,Lia,0,0,0,,Jie Zifang!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:46.06,0:02:47.83,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,（廉頗）介子坊！\N（介子坊）ハッ…
Dialogue: 0,0:02:48.73,0:02:50.14,Kingdom-Main,Lia,0,0,0,,It's over.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:48.83,0:02:50.03,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,終わりじゃ
Dialogue: 0,0:02:51.12,0:02:52.35,Kingdom-Main,Jie,0,0,0,,My lord...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:51.40,0:02:52.44,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,殿…
Dialogue: 0,0:02:52.35,0:02:53.93,Kingdom-Main,Xin,0,0,0,,All right!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:52.57,0:02:54.84,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,しゃ！ 今度こそ…
Dialogue: 0,0:02:53.93,0:02:54.90,Kingdom-Main,Xin,0,0,0,,This time we...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:54.90,0:02:57.65,Kingdom-Main,Lian,0,0,0,,We're making peace, Meng Ao!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:54.97,0:02:57.64,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,和睦じゃ 蒙驁！
Dialogue: 0,0:02:58.28,0:03:00.11,Kingdom-Main,Guy,0,0,0,,Peace...?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:58.58,0:02:59.88,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,（朱可）和睦？
Dialogue: 0,0:02:59.98,0:03:03.65,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,（廉頗）\Nこれより 魏兵への攻撃を禁止する
Dialogue: 0,0:03:00.11,0:03:03.65,Kingdom-Main,Lian,0,0,0,,I hereby forbid any further attacks on State of Wei soldiers!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:04.97,0:03:09.21,Kingdom-Main,Lian,0,0,0,,I will promptly retreat the State of Wei Army!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:05.08,0:03:08.99,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,魏国軍は\Nわしが速やかに退却させる
Dialogue: 0,0:03:09.09,0:03:14.66,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,山陽(さんよう)近辺の住人も 退避させるゆえ\Nこれにも手を出すな
Dialogue: 0,0:03:09.21,0:03:14.67,Kingdom-Main,Lian,0,0,0,,I will also be evacuating the people living in the area of Shanyang, so do not touch them, either!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:15.51,0:03:18.67,Kingdom-Main,Lian,0,0,0,,Make sure you don't loosen the reigns on Huan Ji!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:15.66,0:03:20.46,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,特に 桓騎の手綱を緩めるなよ\Nうぬの責任じゃぞ！
Dialogue: 0,0:03:18.67,0:03:20.38,Kingdom-Main,Lian,0,0,0,,He's your responsibility!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:20.85,0:03:24.46,Kingdom-Main,Guy,0,0,0,,Th-These are peace negotiations?!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:21.00,0:03:24.13,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,こ… これは和睦交渉なのか？
Dialogue: 0,0:03:24.43,0:03:29.11,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,しかし 何の記しもなしに…\Nしかも この場合…
Dialogue: 0,0:03:24.46,0:03:29.22,Kingdom-Main,Guy,0,0,0,,But there aren't any scribes or anything. He's doing it in this situation?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:31.33,0:03:36.56,Kingdom-Main,Ao,0,0,0,,Normally, the winners are the ones that decide the conditions for peace.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:31.54,0:03:36.58,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,和睦の条件とは\N普通 勝者が決めるのじゃがのぅ
Dialogue: 0,0:03:36.86,0:03:38.84,Kingdom-Main,Lian,0,0,0,,Pipe down!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:36.98,0:03:41.92,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,やかましい！\N命があるだけ ありがたいと思え！
Dialogue: 0,0:03:38.84,0:03:42.08,Kingdom-Main,Lian,0,0,0,,You should be thankful that you're\N getting out of this with your life!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:42.70,0:03:45.60,Kingdom-Main,Lian,0,0,0,,Okay, make a quick decision.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:42.75,0:03:46.79,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,さあ 即決せい　さもなくば―
Dialogue: 0,0:03:45.60,0:03:51.20,Kingdom-Main,Lian,0,0,0,,Otherwise I'll have to kill you all before the reinforcements arrive!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:46.92,0:03:51.09,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,新手が来る前に\N貴様ら全員 皆殺しじゃ
Dialogue: 0,0:03:51.89,0:03:56.71,Kingdom-Main,Lian,0,0,0,,Make sure you understand, I'm the one compromising here.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:52.06,0:03:56.70,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,言っておくが譲歩してやってるのは\Nわしのほうじゃぞ
Dialogue: 0,0:03:57.00,0:04:00.10,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,フン… 十分 分かっておるわい
Dialogue: 0,0:03:57.80,0:04:00.21,Kingdom-Main,Ao,0,0,0,,I'm well aware of that.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:05.84,0:04:06.71,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,（蒙驁）フォ…
Dialogue: 0,0:04:07.71,0:04:14.19,Kingdom-Main,Ao,0,0,0,,Understood! I hear the terms for peace as stated by the State of Wei Army representative Lian Po,
Dialogue: 0,0:04:07.88,0:04:13.92,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,相分かった！\N魏国軍代表 廉頗の和睦申し入れ
Dialogue: 0,0:04:14.02,0:04:18.72,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,秦国軍総大将 蒙驁が\N受け入れようぞ！
Dialogue: 0,0:04:14.19,0:04:18.73,Kingdom-Main,Ao,0,0,0,,and as Supreme Commander of the State of Qin Army, I, Meng Ao, accept them!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:18.86,0:04:22.09,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,（どよめき）\Nえっ… これって…
Dialogue: 0,0:04:20.36,0:04:22.24,Kingdom-Main,Xin,0,0,0,,S-So then...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:24.79,0:04:29.35,Kingdom-Main,Narrator,0,0,0,,The establishment of peace signifies the end of a war.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:24.93,0:04:29.13,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,（ﾅﾚｰﾀｰ）\N和睦の成立は 戦の終結を意味する
Dialogue: 0,0:04:30.51,0:04:36.16,Kingdom-Main,Narrator,0,0,0,,In other words, at this moment, the State of Qin's victory was decided.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:30.67,0:04:31.70,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,つまり―
Dialogue: 0,0:04:32.07,0:04:36.07,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,この瞬間\N秦国軍の勝利が決まったのである
Dialogue: 0,0:04:42.81,0:04:44.05,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,（尾平(びへい)）ハッ…
Dialogue: 0,0:04:45.85,0:04:47.88,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,ま… まさか…
Dialogue: 0,0:04:46.52,0:04:47.92,Kingdom-Main,Ping,0,0,0,,Could it be?!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:48.68,0:04:50.93,Kingdom-Main,Pan,0,0,0,,L-Lord Ben.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:48.85,0:04:50.89,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,（番陽(ばんよう)）ほ… 賁(ほん)さま
Dialogue: 0,0:04:52.56,0:04:53.49,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,（王賁）フン…
Dialogue: 0,0:04:54.25,0:04:55.93,Kingdom-Main,Jie,0,0,0,,I humbly apologize.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:54.52,0:04:55.89,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,（介子坊）申し訳ありません…
Dialogue: 0,0:04:55.93,0:05:00.00,Kingdom-Main,Jie,0,0,0,,The cause of our defeat was that I lose track of Huan Ji...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:56.03,0:04:59.90,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,敗戦の責は 桓騎を見失った私に…
Dialogue: 0,0:05:00.00,0:05:02.13,Kingdom-Main,Lian,0,0,0,,It was not Huan Ji.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:00.00,0:05:02.97,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,桓騎ではない\N（介子坊）はぁ？
Dialogue: 0,0:05:02.13,0:05:03.33,Kingdom-Main,Jie,0,0,0,,Sir?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:03.27,0:05:07.57,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,魏国軍の主力にして\N土台であった中央軍
Dialogue: 0,0:05:03.33,0:05:07.70,Kingdom-Main,Lian,0,0,0,,The central army which was the foundation of the State of Wei's main force...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:07.67,0:05:11.51,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,あれが健在ならば立て直しは図れた
Dialogue: 0,0:05:07.70,0:05:11.45,Kingdom-Main,Lian,0,0,0,,If it were still going strong, then we could have devised a regrouping.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:11.86,0:05:18.46,Kingdom-Main,Lian,0,0,0,,The biggest mistake in my calculations was General Lun Hu getting slain by as-of-yet unknown soldiers.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:12.01,0:05:15.25,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,最大の誤算は その将 輪虎が―
Dialogue: 0,0:05:15.55,0:05:18.51,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,まだ無名の者たちに\N討たれたことじゃ
Dialogue: 0,0:05:25.26,0:05:27.46,Kingdom-Main,Lian,0,0,0,,Oh, right.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:25.26,0:05:28.52,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,おお そうじゃった
Dialogue: 0,0:05:34.17,0:05:38.48,Kingdom-Main,Lian,0,0,0,,How about we settle a matter here?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:34.53,0:05:38.53,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,こっちは こっちで\N話をつけておこうかのぅ
Dialogue: 0,0:05:40.40,0:05:42.85,Kingdom-Main,Xin,0,0,0,,Meng Tian, get back.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:40.57,0:05:42.84,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,蒙恬 下がってろ…
Dialogue: 0,0:05:43.93,0:05:45.23,Kingdom-Main,Tian,0,0,0,,Xin...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:44.01,0:05:45.14,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,信…
Dialogue: 0,0:05:49.41,0:05:52.20,Kingdom-Main,Xin,0,0,0,,You want payback for Lun Hu, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:49.68,0:05:52.15,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,輪虎の落とし前ってわけか
Dialogue: 0,0:06:01.08,0:06:02.88,Kingdom-Main,Lian,0,0,0,,What, youngster?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:01.19,0:06:06.00,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,なんじゃ 童(わっぱ)\N貴様 見た目以上に頭が悪いのぅ
Dialogue: 0,0:06:02.88,0:06:06.19,Kingdom-Main,Lian,0,0,0,,You're even dumber than you look.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:06.10,0:06:07.66,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,な… なに！
Dialogue: 0,0:06:06.19,0:06:07.59,Kingdom-Main,Xin,0,0,0,,Wh-What?!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:08.65,0:06:13.59,Kingdom-Main,Lian,0,0,0,,Do Lun Hu or I look like men of such small caliber?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:08.83,0:06:13.67,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,わしや輪虎が\Nそんなに器の小さい男に見えるか？
Dialogue: 0,0:06:14.49,0:06:16.59,Kingdom-Main,Xin,0,0,0,,Then, what?!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:14.70,0:06:16.31,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,じゃ 何の…
Dialogue: 0,0:06:17.47,0:06:20.31,Kingdom-Main,Lian,0,0,0,,You said it before, didn't you?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:17.67,0:06:23.68,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,先ほど申しておったろう\N王騎が 貴様に矛を受け取らせたと
Dialogue: 0,0:06:20.31,0:06:23.60,Kingdom-Main,Lian,0,0,0,,That you received Wang Qi's lance.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:24.47,0:06:29.11,Kingdom-Main,Lian,0,0,0,,That means that you are someone that chases after Wang Qi,
Dialogue: 0,0:06:24.68,0:06:29.09,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,…ということは\N貴様は 王騎の背を追う者
Dialogue: 0,0:06:29.42,0:06:34.11,Kingdom-Main,Lian,0,0,0,,someone that seeks to be a Great General.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:29.69,0:06:34.09,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,大将軍を目指す者\N…ということになる
Dialogue: 0,0:06:34.66,0:06:39.00,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,フッ…\N見るからに その低そうな身分でな
Dialogue: 0,0:06:35.42,0:06:39.04,Kingdom-Main,Lian,0,0,0,,But from the looks of you, you're of pretty low birth, eh?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:39.04,0:06:40.28,Kingdom-Main,Xin,0,0,0,,Low birth doesn't—
Dialogue: 0,0:06:39.13,0:06:42.03,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,身分なんて関係…\N（廉頗）ああ 関係ない
Dialogue: 0,0:06:40.28,0:06:42.51,Kingdom-Main,Lian,0,0,0,,Yeah, it doesn't matter!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:43.04,0:06:45.75,Kingdom-Main,Lian,0,0,0,,What you need in order to become a Great General
Dialogue: 0,0:06:43.13,0:06:47.90,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,大将軍になるために必要なものは\N百の精神力！
Dialogue: 0,0:06:45.99,0:06:47.92,Kingdom-Main,Lian,0,0,0,,is great "force of will"!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:48.92,0:06:50.88,Kingdom-Main,Lian,0,0,0,,And great physical strength!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:49.04,0:06:52.31,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,そして 百の腕力！ 更に 百の知恵
Dialogue: 0,0:06:50.88,0:06:52.42,Kingdom-Main,Lian,0,0,0,,And great wisdom!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:52.64,0:06:56.31,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,それから 百の経験と 百の幸運！
Dialogue: 0,0:06:52.65,0:06:56.43,Kingdom-Main,Lian,0,0,0,,And then you need great experience and great luck!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:56.65,0:06:58.89,Kingdom-Thought,Xin,0,0,0,,Th-That's a lot... {Thought}
Dialogue: 0,0:06:56.88,0:06:58.92,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,（信）お… 多い
Dialogue: 0,0:06:58.89,0:07:06.19,Kingdom-Main,Lian,0,0,0,,The State of Zhao Three Great Devas and the State of Qin Six Great Generals had all of those things.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:59.05,0:07:04.99,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,それら全てを兼ね備えた\N趙国三大天(ちょうこく さんだいてん)と秦国六大将軍は―
Dialogue: 0,0:07:05.09,0:07:09.93,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,かつて\N正に完璧(かんぺき)な時代を築き上げた
Dialogue: 0,0:07:06.19,0:07:09.94,Kingdom-Main,Lian,0,0,0,,And at one time... we constructed the perfect era!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:11.45,0:07:18.37,Kingdom-Main,Lian,0,0,0,,I guess since I'm the only one that survived it, I must have been the strongest!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:11.66,0:07:17.93,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,その中で 唯一 生き残った わしは\N結局 最強だったということかのぅ
Dialogue: 0,0:07:22.17,0:07:24.64,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,まあ それは いいとして
Dialogue: 0,0:07:22.68,0:07:26.21,Kingdom-Main,Lian,0,0,0,,Well, though about that, youngster.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:24.77,0:07:26.64,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,童…\N（信）ハッ…
Dialogue: 0,0:07:26.58,0:07:33.09,Kingdom-Main,Lian,0,0,0,,Do you seriously think you can become my equal?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:26.78,0:07:28.91,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,そんな わしらと 貴様は―
Dialogue: 0,0:07:29.01,0:07:33.05,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,本気で 肩を並べるようになれると\N思っておるのか？
Dialogue: 0,0:07:38.29,0:07:40.76,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,ヘッ… だから 言ってんだろう
Dialogue: 0,0:07:39.03,0:07:40.68,Kingdom-Main,Xin,0,0,0,,I told you, didn't I?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:40.91,0:07:44.01,Kingdom-Main,Xin,0,0,0,,My dream ain't something half-assed like that!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:41.09,0:07:44.76,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,俺の夢は そんな半端じゃねえって\N（廉頗）うん？
Dialogue: 0,0:07:45.52,0:07:47.35,Kingdom-Main,Xin,0,0,0,,I won't be your equal!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:45.73,0:07:47.26,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,肩を並べるんじゃねえ
Dialogue: 0,0:07:47.66,0:07:49.94,Kingdom-Main,Xin,0,0,0,,I'll blow through you guys
Dialogue: 0,0:07:47.90,0:07:53.87,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,俺は あんたらをぶち抜いて\N史上最強の天下の大将軍になるんだ
Dialogue: 0,0:07:49.94,0:07:53.86,Kingdom-Main,Xin,0,0,0,,and I'll become strongest general in all of history under the heavens!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:57.31,0:08:00.24,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,聞いたか？ 介子坊\N（介子坊）はぁ…
Dialogue: 0,0:07:57.36,0:07:59.71,Kingdom-Main,Lian,0,0,0,,Ya hear that, Jie Zifang?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:59.71,0:08:00.44,Kingdom-Main,Jie,0,0,0,,Yes, sir.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:00.34,0:08:03.28,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,いや 悪くないぞ 小僧
Dialogue: 0,0:08:00.44,0:08:03.37,Kingdom-Main,Lian,0,0,0,,Naw, not bad, kid.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:03.37,0:08:09.63,Kingdom-Main,Lian,0,0,0,,For the first time in a while, your intensity made me remember what we were like in our younger days.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:03.41,0:08:09.69,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,今の感じは 久しぶりに若きころの\Nわしたちの姿を思い出した
Dialogue: 0,0:08:11.72,0:08:18.29,Kingdom-Main,Lian,0,0,0,,All right. Seeing as you know so little, I'll tell you something.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:11.89,0:08:17.76,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,よかろう　ものを知らぬ貴様に\Nひとつだけ教えておいてやる
Dialogue: 0,0:08:18.26,0:08:20.90,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,貴様は\Nわしらを追い抜くことも―
Dialogue: 0,0:08:18.29,0:08:25.14,Kingdom-Main,Lian,0,0,0,,It is not possible for you to surpass us or equal us!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:21.36,0:08:25.10,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,わしらと\N肩を並べることも できはしない
Dialogue: 0,0:08:26.02,0:08:27.14,Kingdom-Main,Xin,0,0,0,,What?!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:26.17,0:08:27.10,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,なんだと…
Dialogue: 0,0:08:28.34,0:08:34.32,Kingdom-Main,Lian,0,0,0,,That scorching era is already undeniably the stuff of legend!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:28.44,0:08:34.14,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,強烈すぎた あの時代は\Nもはや かげることなき伝説
Dialogue: 0,0:08:34.24,0:08:38.92,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,故に これから先\Nいかに貴様らが暴れ回ろうと―
Dialogue: 0,0:08:34.32,0:08:39.04,Kingdom-Main,Lian,0,0,0,,So no matter how you bastards rampage across this land,
Dialogue: 0,0:08:39.02,0:08:42.12,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,常に疑問を呈される\N（信）ンッ…
Dialogue: 0,0:08:39.04,0:08:41.66,Kingdom-Main,Lian,0,0,0,,it will always be questioned.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:42.16,0:08:47.66,Kingdom-Main,Lian,0,0,0,,In other words, you'll wonder "How would this have gone if they lived in this era?"
Dialogue: 0,0:08:42.25,0:08:47.72,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,すなわち“彼らが\Nもし この時代にいたならば”とな
Dialogue: 0,0:08:47.66,0:08:52.67,Kingdom-Main,Xin,0,0,0,,W-What?! But there's nothing we can do about that!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:47.86,0:08:52.73,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,そ… そんな！ んなの 俺らには\Nどうしようもねえことじゃねえか
Dialogue: 0,0:08:52.67,0:08:54.61,Kingdom-Main,Lian,0,0,0,,Exactly.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:52.86,0:08:54.43,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,そのとおりじゃ
Dialogue: 0,0:08:54.61,0:08:59.68,Kingdom-Main,Lian,0,0,0,,Our legends are protected by the flow of time.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:54.73,0:08:59.74,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,わしらの伝説は 時の流れに\N守られてしまったからのぅ
Dialogue: 0,0:08:59.87,0:09:02.31,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,ンッ… 証明の…
Dialogue: 0,0:09:00.75,0:09:02.90,Kingdom-Thought,Xin,0,0,0,,There's no way... {Thought}
Dialogue: 0,0:09:02.87,0:09:04.41,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,（蒙恬）しようがない…
Dialogue: 0,0:09:02.90,0:09:04.68,Kingdom-Thought,Tian,0,0,0,,...to prove it. {Thought}
Dialogue: 0,0:09:04.68,0:09:10.19,Kingdom-Main,Lian,0,0,0,,But there is actually one way to surpass us.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:04.87,0:09:10.15,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,じゃが 実は ひとつだけ\Nわしらを抜く方法が存在する
Dialogue: 0,0:09:10.28,0:09:13.35,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,えっ？\Nな… 何だよ？ その方法って
Dialogue: 0,0:09:10.78,0:09:13.44,Kingdom-Main,Xin,0,0,0,,Wh-What is it?!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:14.78,0:09:18.35,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,フッ… 伝説の塗り替えじゃ
Dialogue: 0,0:09:16.09,0:09:18.40,Kingdom-Main,Lian,0,0,0,,Blow away the legends.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:19.24,0:09:23.45,Kingdom-Main,Lian,0,0,0,,If you achieve something great that even we could not achieve,
Dialogue: 0,0:09:19.32,0:09:23.36,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,わしらでも なしえなかった大業を\Nやってのければ―
Dialogue: 0,0:09:23.45,0:09:27.01,Kingdom-Main,Lian,0,0,0,,history will surely revere you!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:23.49,0:09:29.97,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,歴史は 必ず貴様らをあがめる\N（信）なしえなかった大業…
Dialogue: 0,0:09:27.01,0:09:29.96,Kingdom-Main,Xin,0,0,0,,Something great no one's ever done before?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:30.15,0:09:31.45,Kingdom-Main,Lian,0,0,0,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:32.64,0:09:36.40,Kingdom-Main,Lian,0,0,0,,The uniting of China.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:32.90,0:09:36.31,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,中華の統一じゃ
Dialogue: 0,0:09:39.73,0:09:42.89,Kingdom - Episode Title,Sign,0,0,0,,{\fad(400,0)\fs60\be0\pos(490,695)}Xin
Dialogue: 0,0:09:44.16,0:09:47.20,Kingdom-Thought,Xin,0,0,0,,The uniting... of China...? {Thought}
Dialogue: 0,0:09:44.20,0:09:47.13,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,中華の… 統一
Dialogue: 0,0:09:47.20,0:09:52.97,Kingdom-Main,Tian,0,0,0,,Th-That's something a bit too disconnected from reality...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:47.27,0:09:52.94,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,そ… それは…\Nあまりにも現実離れした大業だ
Dialogue: 0,0:09:53.87,0:10:00.21,Kingdom-Main,Lian,0,0,0,,Exactly. It's been 500 years since we entered this world of warring states.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:54.11,0:10:00.15,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,そのとおりじゃ　戦乱の世に\N突入して500年じゃからのぅ
Dialogue: 0,0:10:00.21,0:10:06.20,Kingdom-Main,Lian,0,0,0,,To achieve that, a king with great military power and the caliber to use it...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:00.28,0:10:01.88,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,それを成すには―
Dialogue: 0,0:10:01.98,0:10:06.15,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,すさまじい武の力と\Nそれを振るう器
Dialogue: 0,0:10:06.71,0:10:13.21,Kingdom-Main,Lian,0,0,0,,as well as the caliber to accept the karma of great, bloody deeds must appear.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:06.89,0:10:13.16,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,血の大業の業を受け止める器を\N持つ王が 出現せねばならん
Dialogue: 0,0:10:14.06,0:10:15.40,Kingdom-Main,Tian,0,0,0,,That's impossible.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:14.23,0:10:18.93,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,ムリだ　伝説の武王(ぶおう)をも超える\Nそんな覇業に挑む王など―
Dialogue: 0,0:10:15.40,0:10:19.83,Kingdom-Main,Tian,0,0,0,,There's no way a king that will make a bid for supremacy like that, even surpassing the legendary King Wu, could emerge...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:19.03,0:10:21.33,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,出てくるはずが…\N（信）いや ムリじゃねえ
Dialogue: 0,0:10:19.83,0:10:21.72,Kingdom-Main,,0,0,0,,No, it's not impossible.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:22.00,0:10:24.97,Kingdom-Thought,Xin,0,0,0,,No, it's not impossible, Meng Tian.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:22.17,0:10:24.97,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,ムリなんかじゃねえぞ 蒙恬
Dialogue: 0,0:10:25.77,0:10:31.73,Kingdom-Thought,Xin,0,0,0,,Uniting China. There is someone who has boasted that that is their defined path... {Thought}
Dialogue: 0,0:10:25.94,0:10:31.58,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,“中華統一” それを 自分の確かな\N道だって豪語しやがったのが―
Dialogue: 0,0:10:32.06,0:10:34.73,Kingdom-Thought,Xin,0,0,0,,our current king! {Thought}
Dialogue: 0,0:10:32.31,0:10:34.58,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,今の俺たちの王さまだ！
Dialogue: 0,0:10:36.43,0:10:38.44,Kingdom-Main,Xin,0,0,0,,It's a promise, General Lian Po!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:36.45,0:10:38.38,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,約束だぞ 廉頗将軍！
Dialogue: 0,0:10:40.98,0:10:46.76,Kingdom-Main,Xin,0,0,0,,Uniting China! That'll be proof that we've surpassed you guys!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:41.12,0:10:46.56,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,中華統一！ それが\N俺らが あんたらを超えた証しだ！
Dialogue: 0,0:10:53.63,0:10:55.00,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,ウワッ…\N（どよめき）
Dialogue: 0,0:10:56.80,0:10:59.88,Kingdom-Main,Lian,0,0,0,,Give it your all to devote yourself to that.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:56.97,0:11:01.01,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,せいぜい精進せい　じゃあな
Dialogue: 0,0:10:59.88,0:11:04.01,Kingdom-Main,Lian,0,0,0,,So long, Xin of the Feixin Unit.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:01.57,0:11:04.01,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,飛信(ひしん)隊 信
Dialogue: 0,0:11:06.47,0:11:09.02,Kingdom-Main,Xin,0,0,0,,H-Hey, Lun Hu's sword!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:07.01,0:11:09.02,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,おい！ 輪虎の剣は？
Dialogue: 0,0:11:09.50,0:11:12.52,Kingdom-Main,Tian,0,0,0,,He's clearly telling you to take it.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:09.55,0:11:12.42,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,それは\Nお前が持っとけってことだろう
Dialogue: 0,0:11:15.38,0:11:19.41,Kingdom-Main,Xin,0,0,0,,Oh... I guess so...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:15.42,0:11:16.42,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,そっか…
Dialogue: 0,0:11:17.99,0:11:19.26,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,そうだな
Dialogue: 0,0:11:36.04,0:11:39.50,Kingdom-Main,Lian,0,0,0,,I have nothing to talk to you about.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:36.18,0:11:40.18,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,貴様と話すことなどないわ\N（蒙驁）フォ？
Dialogue: 0,0:11:40.28,0:11:45.92,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,フォフォ… そう言うなて\N公式の和議もろもろ ある
Dialogue: 0,0:11:41.10,0:11:43.10,Kingdom-Main,Ao,0,0,0,,Don't say that!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:43.10,0:11:46.04,Kingdom-Main,Ao,0,0,0,,There are all kinds of peace negotiations.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:46.02,0:11:50.06,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,両軍 少し落ち着いたら\Nそのとき ゆっくり語ろうて…
Dialogue: 0,0:11:46.04,0:11:48.30,Kingdom-Main,Ao,0,0,0,,There are all kinds of formal arrangements to make.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:48.30,0:11:50.01,Kingdom-Main,Ao,0,0,0,,Once both armies have calmed down, we—
Dialogue: 0,0:11:50.01,0:11:52.14,Kingdom-Main,Lian,0,0,0,,Send a representative!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:50.19,0:11:52.46,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,代理を送る\N（蒙驁）フォ？
Dialogue: 0,0:11:53.49,0:11:58.46,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,蒙驁 どういう形にせよ\Nまんまと やりおったな
Dialogue: 0,0:11:53.52,0:11:58.52,Kingdom-Main,Lian,0,0,0,,Meng Ao... In whatever form it may be in, you've squarely beaten me.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:59.36,0:12:03.07,Kingdom-Main,Lian,0,0,0,,There are many major positions across China,
Dialogue: 0,0:11:59.47,0:12:03.07,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,この中華に\N主要拠点は いくつかあるが
Dialogue: 0,0:12:03.41,0:12:06.84,Kingdom-Main,Lian,0,0,0,,but this Shanyang is honestly a huge one.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:03.64,0:12:06.67,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,ここ山陽は誠に でかいぞ
Dialogue: 0,0:12:07.51,0:12:08.68,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,うむ…
Dialogue: 0,0:12:09.11,0:12:16.33,Kingdom-Main,Lian,0,0,0,,My feelings of taking you down for the sake of the State of Wei were not false.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:09.28,0:12:13.65,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,（廉頗）魏国のために 貴様らを\N返り討ちにしてやろうと思ったのは
Dialogue: 0,0:12:13.95,0:12:16.02,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,偽りなき本心
Dialogue: 0,0:12:16.33,0:12:19.46,Kingdom-Main,Lian,0,0,0,,I can't face the state's king now.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:16.42,0:12:19.19,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,国王に合わす顔がないわ
Dialogue: 0,0:12:19.46,0:12:23.34,Kingdom-Main,Ao,0,0,0,,So now you can finally lay down your lance, eh, Lian Po?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:19.52,0:12:23.29,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,これで やっと矛が置けるな 廉頗
Dialogue: 0,0:12:23.66,0:12:26.29,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,フッ… わしのおかげで
Dialogue: 0,0:12:24.55,0:12:26.34,Kingdom-Main,Ao,0,0,0,,Thanks to me!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:30.29,0:12:32.10,Kingdom-Main,Lian,0,0,0,,Don't talk nonsense.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:30.40,0:12:32.10,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,（廉頗）バカを言え
Dialogue: 0,0:12:34.55,0:12:37.82,Kingdom-Main,Lian,0,0,0,,I'll be on active duty until I die!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:34.63,0:12:37.54,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,わしは死ぬまで現役じゃ！
Dialogue: 0,0:12:37.64,0:12:40.11,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,帰るぞ！\N（介子坊）ははっ！
Dialogue: 0,0:12:37.82,0:12:39.05,Kingdom-Main,Lian,0,0,0,,Let's go home!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:39.05,0:12:40.11,Kingdom-Main,Jie,0,0,0,,Yes, sir!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:45.30,0:12:47.53,Kingdom-Thought,Xin,0,0,0,,Uniting China... {Thought}
Dialogue: 0,0:12:45.45,0:12:47.41,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,（信）中華の統一…
Dialogue: 0,0:12:51.24,0:12:54.01,Kingdom-Main,Xin,0,0,0,,You finally did it, eh, General Meng Ao!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:51.35,0:12:53.99,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,ついにやったな 蒙驁将軍
Dialogue: 0,0:12:54.01,0:12:56.39,Kingdom-Main,Xin,0,0,0,,No matter how it happens, a win's a win!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:54.09,0:12:58.26,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,何だって勝ちは勝ちだ\N大逆転じゃねえか
Dialogue: 0,0:12:56.39,0:12:58.51,Kingdom-Main,Xin,0,0,0,,You got your big comeback!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:58.36,0:13:00.23,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,将軍 早く手当てを
Dialogue: 0,0:12:58.51,0:13:00.25,Kingdom-Main,Tian,0,0,0,,General, hurry, your wounds must be tended to.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:00.25,0:13:02.96,Kingdom-Main,Ao,0,0,0,,Wait, wait. Later, later.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:00.36,0:13:03.03,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,待て待て　あとあと\N（信･蒙恬）あっ…
Dialogue: 0,0:13:03.29,0:13:06.47,Kingdom-Main,Ao,0,0,0,,This comes first.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:03.50,0:13:06.43,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,（蒙驁）まずは何より これじゃ
Dialogue: 0,0:13:10.64,0:13:14.64,Kingdom-Main,Ao,0,0,0,,In this war, the State of Qin has been victorious!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:10.67,0:13:15.38,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,この戦 秦国軍が勝利したぞー！
Dialogue: 0,0:13:18.68,0:13:20.35,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,（崇原(すうげん)･松左(しょうさ)）しゃ！
Dialogue: 0,0:13:18.83,0:13:20.40,Kingdom-Main,Guys,0,0,0,,All right!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:20.40,0:13:23.61,Kingdom-Main,Ping,0,0,0,,We did it! We did it!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:20.48,0:13:23.55,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,（尾平）\Nやった！ やったぞ！ ハハハッ！
Dialogue: 0,0:13:24.44,0:13:26.35,Kingdom-Main,Pan,0,0,0,,It's regrettable.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:24.58,0:13:26.05,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,無念です…
Dialogue: 0,0:13:26.35,0:13:31.53,Kingdom-Main,Pan,0,0,0,,If only you had been there, Lord Ben, I am sure you could have rendered some achievements!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:26.35,0:13:31.42,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,あの場に賁さまがおられれば\N必ずや 武功を上げられたはず
Dialogue: 0,0:13:31.52,0:13:32.76,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,（王賁）当然だ
Dialogue: 0,0:13:31.53,0:13:33.12,Kingdom-Main,Ben,0,0,0,,Of course.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:34.16,0:13:39.23,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,だが この地で 激烈な魏国の軍勢を\Nせき止められるのは―
Dialogue: 0,0:13:34.17,0:13:41.42,Kingdom-Main,Ben,0,0,0,,But only the Yufeng Unit was able to halt the fervent State of Wei Army forces here.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:39.33,0:13:41.37,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,玉鳳(ぎょくほう)隊以外なかった
Dialogue: 0,0:13:41.61,0:13:45.30,Kingdom-Main,Ben,0,0,0,,Do not fear. I will not yield next time.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:41.63,0:13:45.07,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,案ずるな　次は譲らない
Dialogue: 0,0:13:47.23,0:13:51.10,Kingdom-Main,Guy,0,0,0,,Boss! It looks like they reached the conclusion!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:47.44,0:13:50.68,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,（手下）\Nお頭！ 決着ついたようですぜ
Dialogue: 0,0:13:51.10,0:13:52.93,Kingdom-Main,Huan,0,0,0,,I can see that on my own.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:51.18,0:13:52.78,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,（桓騎）見りゃ分かるよ
Dialogue: 0,0:13:53.18,0:13:55.70,Kingdom-Main,Huan,0,0,0,,I'm looking forward to the reward.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:53.38,0:13:57.78,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,（桓騎）論功が楽しみだな\N（手下たち）ヘヘヘヘッ…
Dialogue: 0,0:14:01.65,0:14:03.34,Kingdom-Main,Guy,0,0,0,,Lord Jiang Yan.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:01.72,0:14:03.19,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,（副将）姜燕さま…
Dialogue: 0,0:14:03.29,0:14:05.49,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,（姜燕）帰るぞ\N（副将）ははっ…
Dialogue: 0,0:14:03.34,0:14:04.65,Kingdom-Main,Jiang,0,0,0,,We're going home.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:04.65,0:14:05.57,Kingdom-Main,Guy,0,0,0,,Yes, sir!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:10.13,0:14:11.10,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,（王翦）フン…
Dialogue: 0,0:14:11.83,0:14:17.10,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,ハハハッ… すげえ熱気だ\Nもう１戦いけんじゃねえか？
Dialogue: 0,0:14:13.27,0:14:15.48,Kingdom-Main,Xin,0,0,0,,It sure is intense around here!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:15.48,0:14:17.08,Kingdom-Main,Xin,0,0,0,,Kinda feels like you could last another battle, doesn't it?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:17.84,0:14:22.31,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,信 すげえ顔色悪いぞ\Nお前は ここで寝てろ
Dialogue: 0,0:14:17.87,0:14:20.74,Kingdom-Main,Tian,0,0,0,,Xin, your complexion looks really bad.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:20.74,0:14:22.41,Kingdom-Main,Tian,0,0,0,,You should rest here.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:22.41,0:14:23.79,Kingdom-Main,Xin,0,0,0,,Don't be an idiot.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:22.41,0:14:25.51,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,バカ言え\N今から下行って みんなと…
Dialogue: 0,0:14:23.79,0:14:25.54,Kingdom-Main,Xin,0,0,0,,I've gotta head down and celebrate with everyone...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:25.54,0:14:27.84,Kingdom-Main,Bi,0,0,0,,Xin, is that you?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:25.65,0:14:27.71,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,信！ 信か？\N（信）えっ？
Dialogue: 0,0:14:27.85,0:14:30.28,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,あっ！ 壁のあんちゃ…
Dialogue: 0,0:14:28.61,0:14:30.47,Kingdom-Main,Xin,0,0,0,,Brother Bi!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:31.84,0:14:33.80,Kingdom-Main,Bi,0,0,0,,X-Xin! What's wrong?!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:31.85,0:14:33.72,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,（壁）し… 信！ どうした？
Dialogue: 0,0:14:33.80,0:14:35.82,Kingdom-Main,Tian,0,0,0,,He's not breathing?!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:33.85,0:14:38.16,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,（蒙恬）ゲッ！ こいつ 息してない\N救護兵！ 救護兵！
Dialogue: 0,0:14:35.82,0:14:38.18,Kingdom-Main,Tian,0,0,0,,Aid soldiers! Aid soldiers!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:40.94,0:14:44.52,Kingdom-Main,Guy,0,0,0,,R-Report! Report!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:41.19,0:14:42.33,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,（伝令）ほ… 報告！
Dialogue: 0,0:14:42.46,0:14:44.40,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,報告ーっ！
Dialogue: 0,0:14:44.86,0:14:49.40,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,も… 蒙驁軍 勝利！\N蒙驁軍 勝利です！
Dialogue: 0,0:14:44.99,0:14:48.04,Kingdom-Main,Guy,0,0,0,,The Meng Ao Army... is victorious!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:48.04,0:14:49.94,Kingdom-Main,Guy,0,0,0,,The Meng Ao Army is victorious!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:50.67,0:14:51.54,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,（昌文君(しょうぶんくん)）ハァ…
Dialogue: 0,0:14:51.53,0:14:53.13,Kingdom-Main,Guy,0,0,0,,All right!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:51.64,0:14:55.27,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,（廷臣）よ～し！\Nやってくれたな 白老大将軍
Dialogue: 0,0:14:53.13,0:14:55.44,Kingdom-Main,Guy,0,0,0,,The White Elder Great General did it, eh?!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:55.37,0:14:58.54,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,…ということは あの廉頗を！\N（廷臣）ハハハッ！
Dialogue: 0,0:14:55.44,0:14:58.62,Kingdom-Main,Guy,0,0,0,,That means {\i1}the{\i0} Lian Po was...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:58.79,0:15:00.34,Kingdom-Main,Guy,0,0,0,,What a spectacular victory!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:59.11,0:15:01.75,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,大金星だな！\N（廷臣）祝杯じゃ 祝杯！
Dialogue: 0,0:15:00.34,0:15:01.87,Kingdom-Main,Guy,0,0,0,,This calls for a celebratory drink!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:02.33,0:15:03.58,Kingdom-Thought,Chanping,0,0,0,,Good... {Thought}
Dialogue: 0,0:15:02.55,0:15:03.55,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,（昌平君(しょうへいくん)）よし…
Dialogue: 0,0:15:03.58,0:15:06.17,Kingdom-Main,Buwei,0,0,0,,Do you know the details of the war?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:03.68,0:15:08.15,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,（呂不韋(りょふい)）\N戦の詳細は分からんのか？\N武功を上げたのは誰じゃ？
Dialogue: 0,0:15:06.17,0:15:08.14,Kingdom-Main,Buwei,0,0,0,,Who rendered the big achievements?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:08.14,0:15:11.97,Kingdom-Main,Guy,0,0,0,,Yes, sir. It was general Huan Ji sending this information.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:08.29,0:15:11.76,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,（伝令）はっ！\N伝わってきているのは桓騎将軍です
Dialogue: 0,0:15:11.86,0:15:16.30,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,敵の参謀と総大将の２人を討ち取り\N勝利を決したと！
Dialogue: 0,0:15:11.97,0:15:16.43,Kingdom-Main,Guy,0,0,0,,His defeating of an enemy staff officer and their Supreme Commander is what decided the victory!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:16.40,0:15:19.30,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,（呂不韋）\Nおお なんと あの盗賊が？
Dialogue: 0,0:15:16.43,0:15:19.39,Kingdom-Main,Buwei,0,0,0,,Oh. That thief did, eh?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:19.39,0:15:23.14,Kingdom-Main,Guy,0,0,0,,And next is the one that slew the general of the enemy central army, Lun Hu.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:19.40,0:15:23.17,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,（伝令）そして次いで 中央軍の\N将である輪虎を討ち取った―
Dialogue: 0,0:15:23.40,0:15:26.34,Kingdom-Main,Guy,0,0,0,,It was a Thousand-Man General named Xin of the Feixin Unit.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:23.57,0:15:26.74,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,飛信隊の信という千人将です！\N（政(せい)）なっ…
Dialogue: 0,0:15:27.10,0:15:30.15,Kingdom-Main,Buwei,0,0,0,,I don't know who that is, but he did well.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:27.31,0:15:31.64,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,（呂不韋）誰か知らんが\Nようやった ハハハハッ！
Dialogue: 0,0:15:31.74,0:15:33.15,Kingdom-Thought,Zheng,0,0,0,,I see... {Thought}
Dialogue: 0,0:15:31.74,0:15:33.18,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,そうか…
Dialogue: 0,0:15:35.83,0:15:38.29,Kingdom-Thought,Zheng,0,0,0,,You did it, Xin! {Thought}
Dialogue: 0,0:15:36.15,0:15:38.28,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,やったな 信！
Dialogue: 0,0:15:39.27,0:15:41.41,Kingdom-Main,Guy,0,0,0,,H-Honestly?!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:39.45,0:15:41.39,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,（文官）ま… 誠か！
Dialogue: 0,0:15:41.67,0:15:45.88,Kingdom-Main,Guy,0,0,0,,{\i1}The{\i0} General Lian Po was defeated?!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:41.72,0:15:45.26,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,（文官）\Nあの廉頗将軍が敗れたのか？
Dialogue: 0,0:15:45.36,0:15:47.79,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,（カイネ）\Nハッ… 李牧(りぼく)さまの読みが外れた？
Dialogue: 0,0:15:45.88,0:15:47.92,Kingdom-Thought,Kaine,0,0,0,,Lord Li Mu's prediction was off? {Thought}
Dialogue: 0,0:15:49.21,0:15:51.88,Kingdom-Main,Li,0,0,0,,So they took Shanyang, did they?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:49.43,0:15:51.53,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,（李牧）山陽を取られたか…
Dialogue: 0,0:15:52.65,0:15:55.05,Kingdom-Main,Li,0,0,0,,Depending on the State of Qin's attitude,
Dialogue: 0,0:15:52.73,0:15:57.50,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,（李牧）秦国の出方しだいでは\Nここから 天下は大きく荒れますよ
Dialogue: 0,0:15:55.05,0:15:57.46,Kingdom-Main,Li,0,0,0,,there may be some major changes in the world soon.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:58.63,0:16:01.43,Kingdom-Main,Narr,0,0,0,,Having defeated the State of Wei Army,
Dialogue: 0,0:15:58.80,0:16:01.24,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,（ﾅﾚｰﾀｰ）魏国軍を破った秦国軍は
Dialogue: 0,0:16:01.34,0:16:06.81,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,山陽一帯の平定のため 多くが\N臨戦態勢のまま その地に残った
Dialogue: 0,0:16:01.43,0:16:06.58,Kingdom-Main,Narr,0,0,0,,the State of Qin Army left many in that area prepared for battle in order to subjugate the Shanyang region.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:07.18,0:16:11.90,Kingdom-Main,Narr,0,0,0,,Meanwhile, the wounded soldiers started on the road back to the State of Qin.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:07.35,0:16:11.82,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,一方で 傷の重い兵たちは\N秦国への帰路に就いた
Dialogue: 0,0:16:12.24,0:16:17.45,Kingdom-Main,Narr,0,0,0,,And with the Feixin Unit was the modest reward given to them by Meng Ao.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:12.42,0:16:17.42,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,飛信隊が その中に入れられたのは\N蒙驁の ささやかな褒美であった
Dialogue: 0,0:16:18.02,0:16:20.89,Kingdom-Main,Narr,0,0,0,,It was a journey of about one month to reach their home.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:18.19,0:16:20.79,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,故郷までの道のりは およそ ひと月
Dialogue: 0,0:16:20.89,0:16:24.96,Kingdom-Main,Narr,0,0,0,,Though on the way there, many wounded soldiers passed away before they reached their destination.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:20.89,0:16:24.83,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,道中 多くの負傷兵が もたずに\N息を引き取ったが
Dialogue: 0,0:16:24.96,0:16:31.21,Kingdom-Main,Narr,0,0,0,,The soldiers returning home victorious were by no means heavy-footed.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:24.96,0:16:31.24,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,それでも勝者として帰る兵士たちの\N足取りは 決して重くはなかった
Dialogue: 0,0:16:47.79,0:16:50.29,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,（羌瘣(きょうかい)）ンッ… ンン…
Dialogue: 0,0:16:57.60,0:17:00.27,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,そうか 終わったんだな
Dialogue: 0,0:16:57.71,0:17:00.35,Kingdom-Thought,Qiang,0,0,0,,I see. So it's over? {Thought}
Dialogue: 0,0:17:01.05,0:17:05.89,Kingdom-Thought,Narr,0,0,0,,And there was one person saying goodbye in a different way... {Thought}
Dialogue: 0,0:17:01.23,0:17:04.47,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,（ﾅﾚｰﾀｰ）そして\N別の形で別れようとする者が―
Dialogue: 0,0:17:04.87,0:17:05.84,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,ひとり
Dialogue: 0,0:17:07.01,0:17:08.54,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,（昂(こう)）あっ！\N（尾平）羌瘣！
Dialogue: 0,0:17:07.41,0:17:08.70,Kingdom-Main,Ping,0,0,0,,Qiang Lei!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:08.64,0:17:10.24,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,（慶(けい)）羌瘣副長！
Dialogue: 0,0:17:08.70,0:17:10.50,Kingdom-Main,Guy,0,0,0,,Vice Captain Qiang Lei!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:10.50,0:17:12.59,Kingdom-Main,Ping,0,0,0,,You're awake?!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:10.61,0:17:12.41,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,め… 目が覚めたのか
Dialogue: 0,0:17:12.51,0:17:14.88,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,ずっと寝てたんだぞ お前\N大丈夫か？
Dialogue: 0,0:17:12.59,0:17:15.01,Kingdom-Main,Ping,0,0,0,,You were sleeping for a really long time, are you okay?!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:15.84,0:17:18.01,Kingdom-Main,Qiang,0,0,0,,Yeah, fine.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:15.92,0:17:17.88,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,ああ 大丈夫
Dialogue: 0,0:17:18.01,0:17:21.01,Kingdom-Thought,Ping,0,0,0,,S-So cute! {Thought}
Dialogue: 0,0:17:18.02,0:17:20.89,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,（一同）か… かわいい
Dialogue: 0,0:17:21.01,0:17:22.91,Kingdom-Thought,Guys,0,0,0,,She really is cute! {Thought}
Dialogue: 0,0:17:21.02,0:17:24.26,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,（兵士）やっぱり かわいい…\N（兵士）や… やべえぞ
Dialogue: 0,0:17:22.91,0:17:24.39,Kingdom-Thought,Guys,0,0,0,,Aw man, I can't take it!  {Thought}
Dialogue: 0,0:17:24.36,0:17:25.99,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,（兵士）何だ？ この気持ち
Dialogue: 0,0:17:24.39,0:17:26.28,Kingdom-Thought,Guys,0,0,0,,What are these feelings?! {Thought}
Dialogue: 0,0:17:26.28,0:17:29.50,Kingdom-Main,Ping,0,0,0,,Hey, you bastards, don't give Qiang Lei those weird looks!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:26.29,0:17:29.33,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,て… てめえら\N変な目で羌瘣を見るんじゃねえ！
Dialogue: 0,0:17:29.43,0:17:32.57,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,お前だって顔 真っ赤じゃねえか！\N（兵士）そうだ そうだ！
Dialogue: 0,0:17:29.50,0:17:31.65,Kingdom-Main,Guy,0,0,0,,Hey man, your face is bright red!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:31.65,0:17:32.72,Kingdom-Main,Guy,0,0,0,,Yeah, that's right!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:32.67,0:17:33.90,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,アア… うるせえ！
Dialogue: 0,0:17:32.72,0:17:34.02,Kingdom-Main,Ping,0,0,0,,Sheddep!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:36.03,0:17:41.53,Kingdom-Main,Ping,0,0,0,,Um, Qiang Lei, everybody knows you're a woman now...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:36.04,0:17:38.04,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,い… いや 羌瘣
Dialogue: 0,0:17:38.34,0:17:41.51,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,お前が女だってのは\Nもう みんな 知っててさ
Dialogue: 0,0:17:41.53,0:17:45.54,Kingdom-Main,Ping,0,0,0,,We were surprised, but nothing's gonna change because of it.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:41.64,0:17:45.51,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,驚いたけど… 別に\Nだからって 何も変わらねえんだ
Dialogue: 0,0:17:45.54,0:17:48.64,Kingdom-Main,Ping,0,0,0,,Actually, to be honest, I'm kinda glad you're a woman...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:45.65,0:17:48.48,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,逆に 女で良かったっつうか…
Dialogue: 0,0:17:48.58,0:17:53.45,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,実は お… 俺 何度か 自分が\Nそっち系なのかって思うぐらい―
Dialogue: 0,0:17:48.64,0:17:56.35,Kingdom-Main,Ping,0,0,0,,There were actually a few times when I thought I might be uh, {\i1}that way{\i0}, from the weird way I felt when looking at you.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:53.55,0:17:56.29,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,お前のこと見て\N変な気持ちになったことがあって…
Dialogue: 0,0:17:56.35,0:17:58.55,Kingdom-Main,Ang,0,0,0,,What're you talking about, Mr. Ping?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:56.39,0:17:58.52,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,（昂）尾平さん 何言ってんの？
Dialogue: 0,0:17:58.66,0:18:00.53,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,いや だから…
Dialogue: 0,0:17:58.74,0:18:00.55,Kingdom-Main,Ping,0,0,0,,Uh, so...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:00.55,0:18:04.56,Kingdom-Main,Ping,0,0,0,,What I'm saying is everything's still gonna be the same way as always!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:00.66,0:18:04.53,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,とにかく 何もかも\N今までどおりだって言ってんだ！
Dialogue: 0,0:18:05.86,0:18:07.06,Kingdom-Main,Qiang,0,0,0,,Got it.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:05.93,0:18:06.93,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,分かった
Dialogue: 0,0:18:07.40,0:18:09.56,Kingdom-Thought,Ping,0,0,0,,So cute! {Thought}
Dialogue: 0,0:18:07.60,0:18:09.54,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,（一同）かわいい…
Dialogue: 0,0:18:09.56,0:18:13.06,Kingdom-Main,Teng,0,0,0,,Ms. Qiang Lei! Are you going to leave on your journey for revenge?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:09.84,0:18:12.94,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,羌瘣さん！\N敵討ちの旅に行っちゃうの？
Dialogue: 0,0:18:14.16,0:18:18.88,Kingdom-Main,Teng,0,0,0,,Ah, I'm sorry. I heard it from Xin, so I was thinking a lot about it...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:14.41,0:18:18.74,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,あっ ごめんなさい\N信に聞いたから いろいろ…
Dialogue: 0,0:18:20.35,0:18:24.08,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,べ… 別に止めはしねえよ 俺らは
Dialogue: 0,0:18:20.62,0:18:22.95,Kingdom-Main,Ping,0,0,0,,We're not plannin' on stopping you or anything.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:22.95,0:18:28.08,Kingdom-Main,Ping,0,0,0,,Just let us know when you're going. We wanna see you off.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:24.62,0:18:27.95,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,ただ 行くときは言えよな\N見送りてえからよ
Dialogue: 0,0:18:29.22,0:18:30.29,Kingdom-Main,Qiang,0,0,0,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:30.61,0:18:33.23,Kingdom-Main,Qiang,0,0,0,,Wei Ping, where is he?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:30.82,0:18:33.06,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,尾平 あいつは？
Dialogue: 0,0:18:33.23,0:18:34.61,Kingdom-Main,Ping,0,0,0,,Xin?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:33.36,0:18:35.66,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,信か？\N（羌瘣）うん
Dialogue: 0,0:18:36.06,0:18:38.36,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,あいつも ひでえ傷で…
Dialogue: 0,0:18:36.09,0:18:38.34,Kingdom-Main,Ping,0,0,0,,He had some pretty awful wounds, too.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:38.70,0:18:40.68,Kingdom-Main,Ping,0,0,0,,But he's okay now.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:38.83,0:18:40.57,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,でも 大丈夫だ
Dialogue: 0,0:18:40.67,0:18:44.47,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,あと３日もすれば目を覚ますって\N魯延(ろえん)じいが言ってた
Dialogue: 0,0:18:40.68,0:18:44.47,Kingdom-Main,Ping,0,0,0,,Old man Lu Yan said he'd be awake after resting three days.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:46.64,0:18:47.80,Kingdom-Main,Qiang,0,0,0,,I see.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:46.71,0:18:47.74,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,そうか
Dialogue: 0,0:19:07.79,0:19:10.75,Kingdom-Main,Qiang,0,0,0,,Tomorrow, before dawn, I'm leaving.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:07.86,0:19:10.70,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,明日 夜明け前に たつ
Dialogue: 0,0:19:13.68,0:19:16.79,Kingdom-Main,Qiang,0,0,0,,If I head north on a boat floating by on the nearby Yang River tributary,
Dialogue: 0,0:19:13.83,0:19:18.54,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,すぐそこに流れてる羊河(ようが)の支流を\N舟で北上すれば―
Dialogue: 0,0:19:16.79,0:19:21.85,Kingdom-Main,Qiang,0,0,0,,I can go straight to the State of Zhao where my target of revenge is.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:18.94,0:19:21.81,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,敵(かたき)のいる趙国に一気に入れるからだ
Dialogue: 0,0:19:22.44,0:19:26.51,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,…て\N薄暗い中 たつ理由には ならないな
Dialogue: 0,0:19:23.71,0:19:26.51,Kingdom-Main,Qiang,0,0,0,,Though that's not really a reason to leave while it's still dark out.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:29.23,0:19:34.98,Kingdom-Main,Qiang,0,0,0,,I just don't know what sort of face to put on to say goodbye to all of you.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:29.52,0:19:34.92,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,今の私は どういう顔で お前たちと\N別れればいいか分からない
Dialogue: 0,0:19:35.35,0:19:39.02,Kingdom-Main,Qiang,0,0,0,,A long time ago, I used to do things like laugh and cry,
Dialogue: 0,0:19:35.65,0:19:38.92,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,昔は 普通に\N泣いたり笑ったりしてたんだが
Dialogue: 0,0:19:39.02,0:19:44.28,Kingdom-Main,Qiang,0,0,0,,but when I found Big Sis Xiang's corpse, something broke inside me.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:39.06,0:19:44.13,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,象(しょう)姉の亡骸(なきがら)を見つけたときに\N何かが私の中で壊れた
Dialogue: 0,0:19:46.53,0:19:50.49,Kingdom-Main,Qiang,0,0,0,,I hope I go back to normal when I get revenge, but...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:46.73,0:19:49.84,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,敵を討ったら元に戻るといいんだが
Dialogue: 0,0:19:50.47,0:19:52.74,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,まあ …というわけで行く
Dialogue: 0,0:19:50.49,0:19:52.79,Kingdom-Main,Qiang,0,0,0,,Well, anyhow, I'm going.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:54.07,0:19:55.79,Kingdom-Main,Qiang,0,0,0,,Don't think badly of me.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:54.11,0:19:55.47,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,悪く思うな
Dialogue: 0,0:20:01.98,0:20:03.05,Kingdom-Main,Qiang,0,0,0,,See ya.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:01.98,0:20:02.88,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,じゃあな
Dialogue: 0,0:20:13.33,0:20:15.69,Kingdom-Thought,Qiang,0,0,0,,I couldn't get a wink of sleep. {Thought}
Dialogue: 0,0:20:13.53,0:20:15.63,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,一睡もできなかった…
Dialogue: 0,0:20:28.08,0:20:29.45,Kingdom-Main,Xin,0,0,0,,Yup, she fell.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:28.14,0:20:29.48,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,やっぱり落ちた
Dialogue: 0,0:20:31.41,0:20:34.20,Kingdom-Main,Xin,0,0,0,,You think you can get revenge like this?!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:31.61,0:20:34.08,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,こんなんで敵討てんのか？ おい
Dialogue: 0,0:20:34.21,0:20:38.68,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,アハハハッ！\N（渕(えん)）は… 早く羌瘣どのに縄を！
Dialogue: 0,0:20:35.67,0:20:38.33,Kingdom-Main,Yuan,0,0,0,,Q-Quickly, get a rope for Lord Qiang Lei!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:41.61,0:20:44.21,Kingdom-Main,Qiang,0,0,0,,Hey. What the hell are you doing?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:41.65,0:20:44.09,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,何のマネだ？ おい
Dialogue: 0,0:20:44.22,0:20:48.09,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,ヘッ… 罰だ 罰\N黙って１人で行こうとしやがって
Dialogue: 0,0:20:44.84,0:20:48.22,Kingdom-Main,Xin,0,0,0,,That's punishment for trying to go alone without saying anything!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:50.82,0:20:54.94,Kingdom-Main,Xin,0,0,0,,Anyhow, that part of you is really small.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:51.00,0:20:52.10,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,（信）大体…
Dialogue: 0,0:20:52.23,0:20:54.80,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,お前は その辺 ちっせえんだよ
Dialogue: 0,0:20:54.90,0:20:57.70,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,泣こうが笑おうが\Nどっちだっていいっつうの
Dialogue: 0,0:20:54.94,0:20:57.73,Kingdom-Main,Xin,0,0,0,,It doesn't matter if you laugh or cry.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:58.98,0:21:03.73,Kingdom-Main,Xin,0,0,0,,With your heart being so feeble, there's one thing I wanna say to you...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:59.04,0:21:03.71,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,そんな心の かよわいお前に\Nひとつ言っておきてえことはよ
Dialogue: 0,0:21:05.36,0:21:12.62,Kingdom-Main,Xin,0,0,0,,No matter how far away you are, you can bet we're supporting that small frame of yours.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:05.54,0:21:06.98,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,どんだけ離れようと―
Dialogue: 0,0:21:07.08,0:21:12.62,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,お前のちっせえ背中 俺たちが\Nガッチリ支えてるからなってこった
Dialogue: 0,0:21:17.76,0:21:19.66,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,ヘッ… 行ってこいよ
Dialogue: 0,0:21:18.70,0:21:20.17,Kingdom-Main,Xin,0,0,0,,Now get going, Qia—
Dialogue: 0,0:21:19.76,0:21:22.73,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,きょうか… ウワッ！\N（兵士たち）羌瘣ーっ！
Dialogue: 0,0:21:20.17,0:21:22.75,Kingdom-Main,Guys,0,0,0,,Qiang Lei!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:26.39,0:21:27.31,Kingdom-Main,Guys,0,0,0,,Xin!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:27.31,0:21:29.06,Kingdom-Main,Guys,0,0,0,,Lord Xin! Captain!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:29.00,0:21:30.00,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,じゃあな
Dialogue: 0,0:21:29.06,0:21:30.10,Kingdom-Main,Qiang,0,0,0,,See ya.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:30.10,0:21:31.34,Kingdom-Main,Guys,0,0,0,,Good luck!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:36.18,0:21:40.21,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,頑張れよー！\N（声援）
